		<pb n="1"/>
			<p><add>Yiddish</add></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Mr Rev I. Leeser Esq</addressee>&#59;</p>
			<p><add>Yiddish</add></p>
			<p><persName role="author">N. Ottinger</persName></p>
			<p><placeName>161 Division <sic>stret</sic></placeName></p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><add>Yiddish</add></p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><date>Fri<lb/> July 8&#44; 1853</date></p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>Thursday&#44; 2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> Day of<lb/> Rosh Hodesh Tammuz&#44; 1853</date></p>
          <p rend="indent(10)"><addressee>Mr. Rev. I. Leeser Esq.</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I am very much surprised that I<lb/> have not heard from you in so long. I hope<lb/> things are right with you&#44; and that you<lb/> are well. I can say this about myself and<lb/> my family. Thank God.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Again I want some books&#44; namely</p>
			<p>6 prayer&#45;books German ritual</p>
			<p>3&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#8220;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#8220;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Sephardic</p>
			<p>&#160;&#160;bound in usual binding</p>
			<p>3 Pentateuchs of your own in leather<lb/> without gilt</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I hope you will send me everything<lb/> at lowest price. Again I want to be<lb/> advertised in the Occident. Nothing more</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)">With best wishes&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)">your friend&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">N. Ottinger</persName></p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><placeName>161 Division St.</placeName></p>
          
        </body>
